                'title' => 'The Rise of Crypto Payments in Logistics: What It Means for You',
                'slug' => Str::slug('The Rise of Crypto Payments in Logistics: What It Means for You'),
                'excerpt' => 'Cryptocurrency payments are transforming international logistics. Learn how Fast Express Shipping\'s crypto payment options offer speed, security, and global accessibility.',
                'body' => '<p>The global logistics industry has traditionally relied on bank transfers, credit cards, and letters of credit for payment processing — methods that can take days to settle, carry high transaction fees for cross-border payments, and exclude customers in countries with limited banking infrastructure. Cryptocurrency payments are changing this landscape rapidly.</p><p>Fast Express Shipping now accepts Bitcoin (BTC), Ethereum (ETH), and USDT on the TRC20 network. These payment options are available to all customers and offer several distinct advantages: transactions settle within minutes regardless of the sender\'s and receiver\'s countries, fees are significantly lower than international wire transfers, and payments cannot be reversed, eliminating chargeback fraud for our operations.</p><p>For customers in regions where access to international payment methods is limited — parts of Africa, Southeast Asia, and Latin America — crypto payments remove a major barrier to accessing professional shipping services. All you need is a crypto wallet and sufficient funds; no international credit card or bank account is required.</p><p>Security is paramount in our crypto payment process. Each transaction is tied to a unique wallet address generated for that specific shipment. Customers are asked to upload proof of payment, and our finance team verifies transactions on-chain before the shipment is processed. This creates an immutable audit trail for both parties.</p><p>We remain committed to expanding payment accessibility. If you have questions about paying with cryptocurrency or need assistance with the process, our support team is available 24/7 via live chat to walk you through each step.</p>',
