                'slug' => Str::slug('Fast Express Shipping Partners with 200+ Last-Mile Delivery Networks'),
                'excerpt' => 'Our network now includes over 200 last-mile delivery partners worldwide, ensuring reliable final-mile delivery even in areas traditional carriers struggle to reach.',
                'body' => '<p>Last-mile delivery — the final leg of a shipment\'s journey from a local facility to the recipient\'s door — is widely recognized as the most complex and costly part of the logistics chain. Fast Express Shipping has invested heavily in building a diverse network of over 200 last-mile delivery partners across six continents to ensure that our customers receive their shipments reliably regardless of destination.</p><p>Our partner network includes regional courier companies, motorcycle delivery operators for dense urban centers, marine transport providers for island communities, and specialized cold-chain partners for temperature-sensitive shipments. Each partner is vetted through a rigorous qualification process that assesses delivery success rates, customer service quality, tracking system compatibility, and financial stability.</p><p>The benefit to our customers is significant: rather than a one-size-fits-all approach, we can match each shipment to the most appropriate last-mile carrier for its destination. A shipment to rural Kenya may travel via a different partner than one to central London, but both receive the same quality guarantee and real-time tracking visibility through our unified platform.</p><p>Performance is monitored continuously. Our partner management team reviews delivery success rates, average delivery times, and customer satisfaction scores on a weekly basis. Partners who fall below our standards are placed on improvement plans, and those who consistently underperform are replaced. This accountability ensures the network maintains high quality as it grows.</p><p>We continue to add new last-mile partners in underserved regions, particularly in South America, Central Africa, and the Pacific Islands. If you represent a last-mile delivery company interested in partnering with us, please visit our Partner Portal to begin the application process.</p>',
