            [
                'title' => 'New Drop-off Locations Now Available in 50 Additional Cities',
                'slug' => Str::slug('New Drop-off Locations Now Available in 50 Additional Cities'),
                'excerpt' => 'Fast Express Shipping has expanded its physical network with 50 new drop-off locations, making it easier than ever to submit and track your shipments in person.',
                'body' => '<p>We are pleased to announce the opening of 50 new Fast Express Shipping drop-off locations across North America, Europe, and Asia. These locations join our existing network of 300+ drop-off points globally, bringing the total to over 350 convenient spots where customers can submit packages, purchase packaging materials, and receive in-person assistance from trained staff.</p><p>The new locations include 20 sites in the United States concentrated in mid-sized cities in the Midwest and Southeast that previously lacked convenient access, 15 locations across Germany, Poland, and the Czech Republic to serve our growing Central European customer base, and 15 locations distributed across Malaysia, Thailand, and the Philippines in support of our Southeast Asian expansion.</p><p>Drop-off locations offer several advantages over home pickup. Packages submitted at a drop-off point are collected multiple times daily, meaning they enter the transit network faster than scheduled home pickups, which occur once daily at best. Drop-off locations also allow customers to verify packaging with a staff member, purchase on-the-spot insurance, and receive a physical receipt for their records.</p><p>All drop-off locations are equipped with our self-service kiosk system, allowing customers with pre-created online accounts to drop packages in under 60 seconds without waiting in line. The kiosk scans the shipment barcode, weighs the package, and prints a confirmation receipt automatically.</p><p>To find your nearest drop-off location, visit the Locations page on our website or use the location finder in our mobile app. Locations are open seven days a week with extended hours during the holiday season.</p>',
                'published_at' => Carbon::now()->subDays(110),
                'is_published' => true,
