            [
                'title' => 'New Service: Express Pallet Shipping for Small Businesses',
                'slug' => Str::slug('New Service: Express Pallet Shipping for Small Businesses'),
                'excerpt' => 'Fast Express Shipping now offers Express Pallet shipping designed specifically for small businesses that need to move bulk goods quickly without the complexity of full freight contracts.',
                'body' => '<p>Small businesses have long faced a gap in the shipping market: parcel services are not designed for large quantities of goods, while traditional freight services often require minimum volumes, long-term contracts, and complex documentation that is impractical for smaller operations. Fast Express Shipping\'s new Express Pallet service is designed to fill this gap.</p><p>Express Pallet accepts standard 120x100cm pallets weighing up to 500 kg for domestic shipments and 300 kg for international. Transit times are 1–3 business days for domestic routes and 3–7 business days for international, significantly faster than standard LTL freight services. The service includes tracking at the pallet level, so you can monitor your entire pallet\'s journey in real time.</p><p>The submission process for Express Pallet is as simple as our parcel service: enter the dimensions, weight, origin, destination, and content description online, receive an instant quote, and schedule a pickup or drop the pallet at any of our freight-capable locations. No freight broker, no complex Bill of Lading paperwork — our system generates all required documentation automatically based on the information you provide.</p><p>Pricing is transparent and competitive: Express Pallet starts at $150 per pallet for domestic shipments, with international pricing varying by route and weight. Volume discounts are available for businesses shipping 5 or more pallets per month. A flat additional charge applies for pallets with hazardous or oversized contents.</p><p>Express Pallet is already being used by local manufacturers, craft breweries, online retailers, and trade show exhibitors who need to move display materials to venues quickly. If your business regularly ships quantities that exceed parcel limits but you have found traditional freight too cumbersome, Express Pallet may be the solution you have been looking for. Request a demo quote on our website today.</p>',
