                'body' => '<p>Fast Express Shipping is proud to announce that we have been named the winner of the Best Customer Service Award 2024 by the Global Logistics Excellence Association (GLEA). This award recognizes logistics providers that demonstrate exceptional customer service practices as measured by independent customer surveys, response time benchmarks, and complaint resolution rates.</p><p>The evaluation process spanned six months and included mystery shopper assessments, analysis of support ticket response times, customer satisfaction survey data, and direct interviews with business clients. Our team averaged a first-response time of under 12 minutes for live chat inquiries, under 2 hours for email, and a customer satisfaction score of 4.7 out of 5 across all channels.</p><p>We attribute this recognition to the culture of customer ownership our support team has built over the past three years. Every support agent at Fast Express Shipping is empowered to resolve customer issues without escalation in the majority of cases. They have access to real-time shipment data, can initiate claims, issue refunds, and liaise directly with carrier partners — tools that allow them to deliver real solutions quickly rather than just acknowledging problems.</p><p>We are also grateful to our customers for providing honest feedback throughout the year. Every support interaction generates a feedback prompt, and we review low-scoring interactions weekly to identify patterns and training opportunities. This continuous improvement loop is a core part of how we maintain service quality as our business grows.</p><p>Receiving this award is both an honor and a commitment. Our team will continue to raise the bar on customer experience in 2025 and beyond. Thank you to every customer who trusted us with your shipments and took the time to share your feedback.</p>',
